jobs_results.title: Mobile Software Engineer
jobs_results.description:
Role Overview

We are seeking a skilled Mobile Software Engineer to join our team at 10x Beta Venture Studio LLC. This is an exciting opportunity to work on cutting-edge mobile applications using React Native framework and cross-platform technologies.

About Us

10x Beta Venture Studio LLC is a venture studio investing in and incubating connected medical device ventures. We offer a supportive fast-paced environment with the energy of a start-up and the support infrastructure of a mature product design house.

Job Description

As a Mobile Software Engineer, you will be responsible for designing, developing, and maintaining native mobile applications for both Android OS and Apple iOS using React Native framework. You will also work on designing, developing, and maintaining React web applications and web interfaces. Additionally, you will ensure the scalability, performance, and reliability of the web applications, collaborate with cross-functional teams, and translate user needs into technical requirements.

Requirements and Qualifications

To be successful in this role, you should have:
• 4+ years of experience developing with React Native and React
• Knowledge of React / React Native components, APIs, and libraries
• Proven experience in web development with technologies like HTML, CSS, JavaScript, TypeScript, jQuery, JSON, and XML
• Experience with front-end frameworks like Bootstrap
• Experience with CSS and CSS preprocessors
• Experience with responsive and mobile design
• Experience with RESTful and GraphQL APIs, and integrating them into applications
• Experience with software design, object orientation, architecture, and delivery patterns
• Familiarity with refactoring skills and techniques
• An understanding of the mobile ecosystem, common libraries and languages
• An understanding of the full mobile development life-cycle
• Experience in testing automation (unit testing, end-to-end testing)
• Fluency in English

Salary Estimate

The estimated salary for this position is $120,000-$180,000 per year, depending on location and experience. Please note that this is an estimate and may vary based on various factors.

Benefits

As a Mobile Software Engineer at 10x Beta Venture Studio LLC, you can expect a range of benefits, including:
• Flexible working hours
• Opportunities for professional growth and development
• A dynamic and supportive work environment
• A competitive salary and benefits package

How to Apply

If you are a motivated and experienced Mobile Software Engineer looking for a new challenge, please submit your application, including your resume and cover letter.
